      "replayStartSec": 1.617466,
      "replayEndSec": 6.370674,
      "narrationText": "第一步。让我们生成一个新的 ed25519 SSH 密钥。ed25519 是现代默认算法，体积小、速度快、兼容性好。在你将要添加的所有服务器上，这一步只需做一次。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-01.a4774eff.mp3",
      "textHash": "a4774eff7b3ad39178b1ee95c05ee3d542628d140f0e4362d143ca6614f77431",
      "audioDurationSec": 18.755918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-01-after.7346956d.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.04898,
      "afterTextHash": "7346956d4486ff675158dcf40f93218e97015e4d5e278df93d50fc052bcafd1f"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-ssh-keys-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 6.370674,
      "replayEndSec": 13.176828,
      "narrationText": "第二步。用 ssh-copy-id 将公钥复制到服务器。系统会最后一次要求输入服务器密码，此后该服务器就不再需要密码认证了。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-02.60d600db.mp3",
      "textHash": "60d600db6c4a7d0ea91803805915ee9564b7a3342473ef89ea6c08b6ffe6b779",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.747755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-02-after.e08858cd.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.91102,
      "afterTextHash": "e08858cd3d3bd386fad4378187f6f79327e8f7ad1f39689aae88911585f970e3"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-ssh-keys-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 13.176828,
      "replayEndSec": 19.095233,
      "narrationText": "第三步。现在让我们将密钥注册到命令行工具。从此以后，每条命令都使用此密钥进行认证。不再需要密码，不再有交互提示。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-03.ad562073.mp3",
      "textHash": "ad562073617eec5e720222bcb674a6d9c6ba26facd3b26a2b5a1c97932978440",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.31102,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-ssh-keys/tutorial-ssh-keys-03-after.d7e31938.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.115918,
      "afterTextHash": "d7e319380e1470ef300d7684118db387c7a637a47b94527c0489d80bedc8f7be"
    }
